 Adewale Adeleke and Wife Kani Davido’s elder brother and HKN music label chairman, Adewale Adeleke, and his wife, Kani, are now proud parents as they have welcomed a baby girl. The love birds tied the knot in February 2020 in a star-studded wedding that saw a lot of prominent guest from all over Nigeria. In a post on Instagram , the proud father announced the news to his fans that he is now a father of a beautiful girl, with a picture of the little baby’s hand wrapped around his finger, he wrote; “Maya Oluwayemisi Minika Adeleke! Daddy loves you ?????? #GirlDad” The face of the baby has not been revealed yet but we hope to have a glimpse of the child’s face anytime soon.